metadata.name: Obscure Octopus Club #1
metadata.description: For decades our world has been plagued by mysterious disappearances in the Bermuda Triangle . Many say its due to sea conditions and others say that the gravitational pull causes lapse in communication . However, this is far from the truth.A group of creatures, who refer to themselves as a part of the Obscure Octopus Club , have been searching for an ancient treasure which is hidden within the Bermuda Triangle.The OOC has been relentlessly protecting this space. For anyone that enters within the boundaries, they take over their bodies and attain new strengths and skills that can better equip them to find the treasure.For decades they have continued their quest for this search but come empty handed. Are you ready to join the hunt to unravel the biggest underwater mystery?
